HTUNE_A05WC.1.CEN2D.000KCL.nc -> advection centred 2nd order (reference center 4th order)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.L20km.000KCL.nc -> larger domain 20x20km?? instead of 10x10km??
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RK4B2.000KCL.nc -> much stronger white noise th'=0.5K (ref=0.01K)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RK4BB.000KCL.nc -> stronger white noise th'=0.1K (ref=0.01K)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RK4DT.000KCL.nc -> smaller timestep (0.5s instead of 1s)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RK4DZ.000KCL.nc -> higher vertical resolution
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RK4RE.000KCL.nc -> reference simulation
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RK4TU.000KCL.nc -> other length scale formulation for turbulence (delt instead of Deardorff)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RKD25.000KCL.nc -> finer horizontal resolution (25m instead of 50m)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RKD30.000KCL.nc -> larger coefficient for numerical diffusion (300s instead of 1800s)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RKD72.000KCL.nc -> smaller coefficient for numerical diffusion (7200s instead of 1800s)
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RKw3b.000KCL.nc -> advection WENO 3rd order
HTUNE_A05WC.1.RKw5b.000KCL.nc -> advection WENO 5th order (reference center 4th order)
